<div class="subtitle">Add your Reports</div>
<a class="leftimg" href="edit.php"><img src="img/layout.gif" border=0 ></a>
To add your Report :
<ul>
<strong>Go to "Add your REPORT" </strong>
<ul><li>Select your username</li>
<li>Select the week</li>
<li>Select the year</li>
<li>Select the categories you want to edit</li>
</ul>
<br/>
<strong>Then you can edit your report</strong>
<ul>
<li>Edit the Text Area <em>(if you already have a report registered, you can change it by editing his content)</em></li>
<li>Specify a url where the application can get your reports <br/><em>for instance: http://a_web_site/~mylogin/repors/2003/mylogin_35.html</em><br/>
<em>if you are used to put it in your web pages</em></li>
<li>Or directly by uploading a local file</li>
</ul>
<strong>Don't forget to specify the way you add your report: (Text | Url | LocalFile)</strong>
</ul>

